2. Replace `groupByCategory` body with Map-based O(n) implementation
3. Replace `findDuplicates` body with Map-based O(n) implementation
4. Replace `calculateRunningBalance` body with filter-once/sort-once/single-pass implementation
5. Replace `topSpenders` body with Map-based O(n) + native sort implementation
6. Replace `searchTransactions` body with single-compile RegExp + `Array.filter()` implementation
7. Leave `processAll` unchanged (imports and signature unchanged throughout)

---

